Revlon in joint venture in China . Revlon Inc ' s Revlon Consumer Products Corp said Tuesday it entered a joint venture agreement with Sumstar Group Corp , a Beijing - based investment firm , to manufacture , distribute and market Revlon products in China . Distribution of the company ' s products in major cities throughout China should begin in the first quarter of 1997 , and office headquarters and manufacturing facilities will be located in Shanghai , Revlon said . 
